    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and rod bearings have been replaced as a proactive measure. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no perceptible paint depth variance, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. Featuring the M-Variable Differential Lock and a perfectly calibrated suspension geometry, this M3 delivers the raw, analog feedback sought by purists. It is free of any fluid seepage or diagnostic faults, representing a turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
